    "en": [
      { "type": "paragraph", "text": "Acne is a common skin problem. TCM believes acne formation relates to lung heat, spleen-stomach damp-heat, liver stagnation, etc. Treating acne requires not just external medication but internal constitution regulation for root-and-symptom treatment." },
      { "type": "heading", "text": "TCM Understanding of Acne" },
      { "type": "paragraph", "text": "TCM calls acne \"fen ci\" or \"cuo chuang,\" believing its formation relates to:" },
      { "type": "subheading", "text": "Lung Meridian Wind-Heat" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Acne mostly on face", "Accompanied by redness, swelling, heat, pain", "Common in adolescence", "Treatment: Clear lung, dissipate heat"] },
      { "type": "subheading", "text": "Spleen-Stomach Damp-Heat" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Acne with oily secretion", "Mostly around mouth", "Accompanied by bad breath, constipation", "Treatment: Clear heat, resolve dampness"] },
      { "type": "subheading", "text": "Liver Stagnation" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Acne related to emotions", "Worsens under stress", "Common in women", "Treatment: Soothe liver, resolve stagnation"] },
      { "type": "heading", "text": "Internal Acne Treatment Methods" },
      { "type": "subheading", "text": "Clear Lung, Dissipate Heat" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Pi Pa Qing肺饮: Classic lung-clearing formula", "Mulberry bark: Clears lung, drains fire", "Scutellaria: Clears heat, detoxifies", "Honeysuckle: Clears heat, detoxifies", "Chrysanthemum: Clears liver, brightens eyes"] },
      { "type": "subheading", "text": "Clear Heat, Resolve Dampness" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Coix seed: Strengthens spleen, resolves dampness", "Poria: Drains dampness, strengthens spleen", "Coptis: Clears heat, dries dampness", "Artemisia capillaris: Clears heat, resolves dampness", "Mung bean: Clears heat, detoxifies"] },
      { "type": "subheading", "text": "Soothe Liver, Resolve Stagnation" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Rose: Soothes liver, regulates Qi", "Bupleurum: Soothes liver, resolves stagnation", "Curcuma: Moves Qi, resolves stagnation", "Xiao Yao San: Soothes liver, strengthens spleen"] },
      { "type": "heading", "text": "External Acne Treatment Methods" },
      { "type": "subheading", "text": "Herbal External Application" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Honeysuckle water: Clears heat, reduces inflammation", "Coptis powder: Clears heat, dries dampness", "Dandelion water: Clears heat, detoxifies", "Aloe gel: Anti-inflammatory, soothing"] },
      { "type": "subheading", "text": "Acne-Treating Acupoints" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Quchi: Clears heat, detoxifies", "Hegu: Clears heat, dissipates wind", "Feishu: Clears lung, dissipates heat", "Dazhui: Clears heat, releases exterior"] },
      { "type": "recipe", "title": "Heat-Clearing Acne Tea", "ingredients": ["Honeysuckle 10g", "Chrysanthemum 10g", "Dandelion 10g", "Licorice 5g", "Water 500ml"], "instructions": "1. Wash all ingredients\n2. Boil water\n3. Simmer for 10 minutes\n4. Drink as tea\n5. Once daily\n6. Clears heat, detoxifies, treats acne" },
      { "type": "heading", "text": "Acne Diet Restrictions" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Reduce spicy foods: Chili, BBQ, fried foods", "Reduce sweets: Sugar promotes sebum secretion", "Reduce greasy foods: Worsens damp-heat", "Reduce alcohol: Alcohol irritates skin", "Eat light foods: Vegetables and fruits"] },
      { "type": "heading", "text": "Acne Lifestyle Habits" },
      { "type": "list", "items": ["Keep face clean: Gentle washing", "Avoid squeezing: Prevent infection and scarring", "Regular routine: Avoid late nights", "Emotional balance: Stay happy and relaxed", "Moderate exercise: Promotes metabolism and detox"] },
